
---

## 2. Initialize Git and push to GitHub

cd motivation-telegram-bot

# 1. Initialize git
git init

# 2. Create main branch name (optional if already on main)
git branch -M main

# 3. Add remote (create the repo on GitHub first via github.com/new)
git remote add origin https://github.com/Montezace/motivation-telegram-bot.git

# 4. Stage and commit
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit: motivation telegram bot"

# 5. Push
git push -u origin main
